nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Dr. Person1,    Hope you and your family are doing well. I have a close friend who had a hysterectomy, cancer, removed three weeks ago at Org4. She now wants to change any further concerns, such as she was told radiation. Can you tell me how to get her records over to your facility and recommend a good radiology specialist she can see to discuss further.
